*prepei na ftiaxoume filtro pou px na emfanizzei mono tou technicians apo olous tous employees 

---views---
  ---Employees---
  *na emfanizetai kapoio idiaitero haraktiristiko otan patame kapoion, px Iren Vlassi ki ohi Update an Employee
  ---buttons---
  *sth insert to cancel vgainei apo katw apo to submit alla fainetai na kanei swsth douleia, action sto views ki ohi sto models, opws mallon ua eprepe
  *morfopoihsh buttons to ti grafoun pws ktl

---css---
*allagh sto footer na allazei mono tou th thesh tou gia na phgainei parakatw otan megalwnei enas pinaks
*allagh hrwmatos h kati opou eimaste gia na to ksehwrizoume
*morfopoihsh apo to styles.css to <table> , dhladh olous tous pinakes
*ta edit - x stous pinakes isws hwris grammoula anamesa
*morfopoihsh twn <h2>


---genika---
*den einai me proteraiothta oi douleies
*na xeroume pote einai sto server h kathemia giati einai ligo lepto to thema me to syhronismo
*an eiste se vim to control+N sou emfanizei ta pithana auto-complete pou vriskontai ekei konta
